{"tid":1680591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：從未與暴力衝擊的勇武人士對話","createTime":"2019-10-29T02:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T15:05:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":43,"dislike":257,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"e546f9a54ede6f80da633ad6fbf7fc34bf91fec2","tid":1680591,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:14:37.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，在展開社會對話至今，有以不同形式會見不同人士，但並無與暴力衝擊，破壞社會安寧的勇武人士進行過深度對話。她指雖然對話過程，無問及參加者的立場，但出席者亦無提出過，有進行過「勇武」行為。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又強調，支持警隊依法止暴的立場堅定，指警方長時間面對壓力，大部分警員每日要執勤十多小時。她過去曾多次探望警方及交流，有個別警員曾指，不怕流汗或流血，但不希望流淚，不想每日工作期間，需要擔心家人人身安全或會否被起底。她會繼續要求所有政府部門配合警隊工作。"},{"pid":"2f0a6e01590b4c2dd51d584d47680157ea2e6ca5","tid":1680591,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:14:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1195415&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1195415%26csid%3D261_341&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=5462b9e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1195415&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"08ba86d903dd273f533e44ee9922a4da40578586","tid":1680591,"uid":47605,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"我們早前在Telegram成立了手足匿名搵工平台，助手足自行尋找明白其情況的本地良心僱主，幫助他們在漫長保釋（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期）或長期夢境中，有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=fc6036ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a779a1e97dd621287a3b732b251892444f32c4","tid":1680591,"uid":3454,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score